00:11:52.362 --> 00:11:56.462
Ali sada, kad sam ga video,
žao mi ga je.

00:11:59.262 --> 00:12:04.062
Bićemo dobri prema njima,
ako oni budu dobri prema nama.

00:12:04.362 --> 00:12:07.162
Ssskinite nam to.

