00:12:32.562 --> 00:12:34.562
... na Prekrasssnog!

00:12:34.662 --> 00:12:36.862
Golum... Golum.

00:12:37.062 --> 00:12:41.162
Prsten je opasan.
Držaću te za reč.

00:12:42.062 --> 00:12:43.362
Da...

00:12:43.962 --> 00:12:46.362
... na Prekrasnog.

00:12:48.762 --> 00:12:51.162
Na Prekrasnog.

00:12:52.362 --> 00:12:54.862
Ja ti ne verujem!

00:12:55.862 --> 00:12:59.362
Silazi dole! Rekoh, silazi!
-Seme!

